data.description: You will love this charming 3 bedroom/2 bathroom pool home in the desirable area of Holiday Pines! Featuring an open and spacious floor plan, with a family room and a large fireplace; perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with your family. The kitchen has been remodeled with a new dishwasher, stove and microwave; granite countertops; and a view that overlooks the golf course. The adjacent dining area is perfect for family meals or hosting dinner parties. This home is also perfect for outdoor entertaining, with a large, screened patio and pool, with a fenced yard. Upgrades to the home include recently installed impact windows and sliding doors; remodeled pool; new ceiling fans; and freshly painted house interior/exterior.
